### 6. Engine Domain

#### [MODIFY] [AllocationService.java](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/바탕%20화면/민성/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/engine/AllocationService.java)
